-- Citigroup falls after results, CFO comments
-- 
-- Fri Apr 17, 2009 9:19am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/04/17/us-markets-stocks-citi-sb-idUSTRE53G27Q20090417

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Citigroup fell 2.7 percent to $3.90 in premarket trade after initially climbing more than 15 percent after the third-largest U.S. bank posted first-quarter results and comments from the company's chief financial officer. 

 (Reporting by  Chuck Mikolajczak ; Editing by  James Dalgleish )